ca.team3161.iapetus

Class Shooter

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.team3161.lib.robot.Subsystem
      • ca.team3161.iapetus.Shooter

  • public class Shooter
extends Subsystem
    Class needs to control: victor (winch) gauged by linear potentiometer (magnetopot), solenoid (super shifter for gearbox), solenoid (for pickup), talon (roller), talon (fork) Basic Overview Shooter: Init: piston locked, motor cocked back Auto: fork adjust, roller up, piston release, time delay, piston lock, winch motor activate Pickup Mode: fork piston down, roller down, roller motors activate Travel mode: roller motors off, roller down, fork up
